languages.text: "Я знаю, что ты наблюдаешь за мной, Вени'Хейнрикс. Не как друг, но как страж. Я не против".
"I know that you are watching me, Veni'Heinrix. Not as a friend, but as a sentry. I do not mind."

languages.text: "Ich weiß, dass Ihr mich beobachtet, Veni'Heinrix. Nicht als Freund, als Wächter. Ich habe nichts dagegen."
languages.original_text: "I know that you are watching me, Veni'Heinrix. Not as a friend, but as a sentry. I do not mind."

traits.locale_text: "Ich weiß, dass Ihr mich beobachtet, Veni'Heinrix. Nicht als Freund, als Wächter. Ich habe nichts dagegen."

languages.text: « Je sais que vous m'observez, Veni'Heinrix. Pas comme un ami, mais comme une sentinelle sur le qui-vive. Et cela ne me dérange pas. »
languages.original_text: "I know that you are watching me, Veni'Heinrix. Not as a friend, but as a sentry. I do not mind."

traits.locale_text: « Je sais que vous m'observez, Veni'Heinrix. Pas comme un ami, mais comme une sentinelle sur le qui-vive. Et cela ne me dérange pas. »

languages.text: «Ya sé que me vigila, Veni'Heinrix, y que es como centinela y no como amigo. No me importa».
languages.original_text: "I know that you are watching me, Veni'Heinrix. Not as a friend, but as a sentry. I do not mind."

traits.locale_text: «Ya sé que me vigila, Veni'Heinrix, y que es como centinela y no como amigo. No me importa».

languages.text: 「私を見ているのは知っています、ハインリックス。友達としてではなく、歩哨として。私はそれでもかまいませんが」
languages.original_text: "I know that you are watching me, Veni'Heinrix. Not as a friend, but as a sentry. I do not mind."

traits.locale_text: 「私を見ているのは知っています、ハインリックス。友達としてではなく、歩哨として。私はそれでもかまいませんが」

languages.text: “我知道你在留意我，帷者海因里希，那不是朋友的目光，而是哨卫的目光。我并不介意。”
languages.original_text: "I know that you are watching me, Veni'Heinrix. Not as a friend, but as a sentry. I do not mind."

languages.text: "Beni izlediğini biliyorum Veni'Heinrix. Arkadaş olarak değil, gözcü olarak izliyorsun. Sorun etmiyorum."
languages.original_text: "I know that you are watching me, Veni'Heinrix. Not as a friend, but as a sentry. I do not mind."
